data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!  Charming 4 bedrooms, 2 baths open floorplan with a BONUS study perfect for office or formal dining room.  Built by D.R. Horton and only one owner since purchased in 2019.  Updated kitchen features large granite countertop and stainless steel appliances.  Spacious master with garden tub, separate shower, double vanities and walk-in closet.  This house features a water softener installed 2 years ago.  Magnolia Meadows is a popular subdivision that offers pool, playground and basketball area.   Don't pass this opportunity to live in a place where you can see B&B Theatres within minutes, a new upscale, state-of-the-art cinema in Red Oak coming soon!
